<h3 id="configuring-php-file">Configuring PHP File</h3>
<p>And now for the most important part, we will be configuring the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">info.php</code> so it can speak with our database.</p>
<div class="language-console highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
