<p>Let‚Äôs edit our e-mail template to seem like Tony Stark is getting his account mass reported. (Instructions for what should be edited can be found in the HTML).</p>

<p>The main thing we going to focus on is the login button, let‚Äôs copy and paste in our <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ngrok</code> link that we received so it redirects the victim to our site on click.</p>

